{
  "chapter": 4,
  "chapter_summary": "本章讲述萧秋水等人找到捕头何昆带路到巨石横滩，发现铁腕神魔傅天义正在垂钓。何昆突然刚到，以会友身份刺伤唐柔，露出‘无形’真身。唐柔临死前用唐家暗器击中何昆，同当就死。萧秋水、邓玉函、左丘超然三人联手与傅天义展开激战，终于将其击落江中。返回萧家后，唐大、康出渔、朱侠武等人到访，征求一致对抗权力帮。萧秋水发现唐柔尸首上插着自己的剑锶，被嫌疑杀人，但唐大明察秀科，证明萧秋水清白。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么地方是‘巨石横滩’？",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "找个人来问问。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不，以免打草惊蛇，我们叫个熟人带我们去。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "捕头何昆。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咿呀",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_kun",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "诸侠风雨来访，不知是……",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知道何处是‘巨石横滩’？",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_kun",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "知道。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁腕神魔现在就在那儿！",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_kun",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，我带你们去。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "轰卤一声，又是一道闪电，风四处乱吹，有窒息的压迫感，然后雨就疾打下来了，开始是",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "九龙奔江",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_tian_yi",
      "speaker_name": "那老更白眉白须，玄衣如铁，坐在江水飞浪、奔流怒潮的巨石临江，纹风不动，连眼也不抬一下",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们来了？",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "邓玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们来了。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_tian_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁腕神魔淡淡地",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我手边死了三个人，你们可以填补上。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然摇头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "假如我们不愿意呢？",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们不会不愿意的吧？",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_rou",
      "speaker_name": "唐柔平平静静地",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们不是不愿意，而是不肯。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_tian_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁腕神魔仰天大笑，如怒涛江水，鬼位神号",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们岂是我敌手？",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "白天，长江激流，一双铁手，独撑画舫，好强的内力，好深的功夫，萧秋水忽然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "以一敌一，我们不是你的对手，但若以四战一，你绝对占不到便宜。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_tian_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁腕神魔脸色一沉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你以为你有四个人？",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水昂然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是以为，而是事实。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_tian_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁腕神魔又在巨石上，仰天怒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如果我叫你们少一人呢？",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水淡淡地",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不会少的。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_tian_yi",
      "speaker_name": "他们四人并立在一起，在风雨中，在怒涛中，在行雷闪电里，他们是那么英勇，那么无畏，那么生死同心……铁腕神魔目光也闪了闪，竟闪过一丝孤寂，但随即又变得狰狞狂暴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！自古唐家暗器最难防，先毁了他！",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "霹雳",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "邓玉函刷地拔出了玉剑，嘶声叫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刷",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你，你就是‘无形’？",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_xing",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对，我就是‘无形’。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_rou",
      "speaker_name": "唐柔身子开始发软，他慢慢地曲倒下去，一面似笑非笑他说",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没料到我死在你手上。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_xing",
      "speaker_name": "无形赶紧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无形",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_xing",
      "speaker_name": "无形赶紧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也没料到。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_rou",
      "speaker_name": "唐柔已快蹲到地上了，还",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不想死埃",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_rou",
      "speaker_name": "唐柔已快蹲到地上了，还",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无形",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_rou",
      "speaker_name": "唐柔已快蹲到地上了，还",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还是安息吧。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_rou",
      "speaker_name": "唐柔已经趴在地上了，不过他柔弱的话还是勉强可听得到",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不过……唐家的晴器却是有毒的，你……也跟我一齐去吧！",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_xing",
      "speaker_name": "这次无形笑不出了，垂下了伞，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无形",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_xing",
      "speaker_name": "这次无形笑不出了，垂下了伞，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道你是例外。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_rou",
      "speaker_name": "唐柔说完了这句话，就闭了眼睛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我对你，也是例外。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
