      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_rou",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他……他搜我的身，没有人……没有人敢碰未死的唐家人……",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水见他衣衫尽红，嘴角挂了一道血丝，心痛如焚地",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是的，是……",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水见他衣衫尽红，嘴角挂了一道血丝，心痛如焚地",
