      "text": "权力帮",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "然而萧秋水却在此次秭归之行，与南海邓玉函、蜀中唐柔、左丘超然杀了权力帮座下九天十地、十九人魔之一地魔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "权力帮",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "然而萧秋水却在此次秭归之行，与南海邓玉函、蜀中唐柔、左丘超然杀了权力帮座下九天十地、十九人魔之一地魔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "九天十地、十九人魔",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "然而萧秋水却在此次秭归之行，与南海邓玉函、蜀中唐柔、左丘超然杀了权力帮座下九天十地、十九人魔之一地魔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "地魔",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小人物",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "君临天下",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "九龙奔江",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁腕神魔",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无形",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "泰山高，不及东海劳",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "东海劳",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "观日台",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "观日剑",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "万里赴戎机，关山渡若飞，朔气传金析，寒光照铁衣，将军百战死，壮士十年归",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "关云长千里走单骑",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "汉寿亭俟颖，幡龙巨柱之一角，还架把著名天下",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "观日剑",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "我们万万没有想到那差役就是‘无形’，等到知道时，唐柔受到暗算，唉，不过唐柔还是唐柔，唐柔还是用唐家的暗器，杀‘无形’……左丘超然也叹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们万万没有想到那差役就是‘无形’，等到知道时，唐柔受到暗算，唉，不过唐柔还是唐柔，唐柔还是用唐家的暗器，杀‘无形’……",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你这次没去，真是可借。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "连邓玉函也不禁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "与傅天义之战，是我有生以来最惊险的一役。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水接",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可惜唐柔死了……一个是唐柔，一个是唐刚，都是唐家堡年轻一代的高手。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_jie_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "康劫生忽然截",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看今天的事，想必与唐柔的死，有些关系。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水一呆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事情？",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_jie_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "康劫生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "四川蜀中，唐门唐大，他也来了。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大爷",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_rou",
      "speaker_name": "最后一次提起唐大，却是在唐柔杀却何昆之后，在乱石横江前挣扎说出最后的话",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "假如……假如你见到我们的家里……唐大……你代我问他……为何我们唐家……不结成天下……天下第一家……而要让‘权力帮’这些……这些鼠辈横行……",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_rou",
      "speaker_name": "最后一次提起唐大，却是在唐柔杀却何昆之后，在乱石横江前挣扎说出最后的话",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我跟唐大侠禀明此事。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_jie_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "康劫生也站起来",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不能去。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水问",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_jie_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "康劫生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为唐大是抱着一样物事进来的。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水一怔，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么物事？",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁腕神魔",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水举步",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论如何，我们还是要请唐大侠清楚这件事，我们错处，凭他处置。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_jie_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "康劫生还是拦在身前，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不能去。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水奇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_jie_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "康劫生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为唐柔胸前插着一柄剑愕。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水奇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唐柔是背后中何昆一刀致命的。，，邓玉函接道：",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那时就连剑愕也给傅天义连人掉到江里去了！",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那剑不是何昆的，",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "剑愕上着‘萧’字，然后一字一句地道，",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "康劫生看着发愕中的萧秋水，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你的剑呢？",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁腕神魔",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "浣花剑派",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "乱红飞过秋千去",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水涩声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我怎么会杀唐柔！？",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_jie_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "康劫生叹了一口气，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我相信，可是他们会相信吗？",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唐家堡的人会相信吗？",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我可以为萧秋水证明。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们是亲眼看见。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好。只不过唐大若认为萧秋水杀了唐柔，同样也不认为你们脱离得了关系。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论如何，我们还得去见唐大侠。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "况且萧西楼要他出门之前还告诫过他",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "权力帮",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "权力帮",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "九天十地，十大人魔",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然禁不住问",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "厅里究竟有几人？",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_jie_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "康劫生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "萧世伯、伯母、唐大侠、家师、还有朱叔叔。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "浣花剑派",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "十字慧剑",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_jie_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "康劫生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朱叔叔——朱侠武叔叔。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁衣铁手铁脸铁罗网",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "该杀",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼怒极，一时找不到话说，哑声说了一声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你好啊！",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "偏偏萧秋水不知萧西楼这一问是什么意思，忙答",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孩儿此很好。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "喀哟",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好哇！老子给小子问起好来了！",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧夫人忙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "秋水，还不向几位伯伯赔罪！",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼顿足",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你这一趟出去，干什么来着！",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水坚然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我没有杀唐柔！",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你的剑呢？",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "掉了。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "掉了，掉了。你看掉在谁的身上了！",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我真的没有杀唐柔！",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是你杀是谁杀！",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧劫生拉拉萧秋水前袖，悄声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我师父。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "禀康师伯，杀唐柔者，是‘无形’。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无形？无形！",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "畜生，敢对长辈贫嘴！",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_da",
      "speaker_name": "忽然一入",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唐柔不是他杀的。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼反而一怔，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唐大侠说什么？",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杀唐柔的不是秋水兄弟。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "何出此言？",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_da",
      "speaker_name": "唐大",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "秋水兄弟要杀唐柔，也不致要杀尽唐家堡的人。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_da",
      "speaker_name": "唐大",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "秋水兄弟若杀唐柔后，还留下剑愕。那除非他杀尽唐门中人。否则唐家堡只要剩下一人，剩一口气，也要找杀人者偿命。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就算唐柔与秋水兄弟有怨，唐家堡与他也没仇。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "况且我听唐柔提过秋水兄弟的名字。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "像唐柔那么好的孩子，他说秋水兄弟是他最佩服的兄长，那一定不会有错的。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "speaker_name": "康出渔沉思良久，终于",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唐大侠有理。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哼",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唐大侠",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁衣铁手铁脸铁罗网",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_da",
      "speaker_name": "唐大静静地问了一句",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那唐柔是谁杀的？",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_da",
      "speaker_name": "唐大皱眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无形？",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "‘无形’是傅天义手下四大高手之一。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "邓玉函接",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "傅天义就是‘铁腕神魔’",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然也",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁腕神魔，就是‘九天十地、十九人魔’之一",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "刚刚缓和的空气忽然又凝肃了起来，整个大厅都像崩住了一般，好一会萧西楼重复问了一句",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "九夭十地、十九人魔？",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "刚刚缓和的空气忽然又凝肃了起来，整个大厅都像崩住了一般，好一会萧西楼重复问了一句",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是，权力帮座下‘九天十地，十九人魔",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "权力帮",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼忽然笑着朗声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "承蒙诸位兄台远道而来。现在事情已一清二楚，杀唐柔的是‘无形’，指使‘无形’杀唐柔的是傅天义，傅天义为秋水等所杀，这件事已与诸位毫无关系，劳驾诸位来敝庄，现刻事情已水落石出，各位就请回吧，他日萧某幸存，必当登门拜谢。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "诸位，老夫倦矣，不远送了。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "萧兄，你当咱们是什么人了！这事儿咱们听见了，便与咱们有关，在这里，谁也脱不了关系。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "康兄又何必……",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_da",
      "speaker_name": "唐大忽然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "萧大侠，我唐大与你，是不是朋友？",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_da",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼没有作声。唐大",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我再问一声，要是没有回答，我这就离开剑庐，自己去挑‘权力帮’。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是！当然是！",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "萧大侠你赶我也不走了，我与你的儿子已是朋友了。为了朋友两肋插刀，在所不辞，这是古已有道的。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朱大侠看来也不走的了。有咱们几个，看来还可以与‘权力帮’耗耗力气。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_da",
      "speaker_name": "唐大微笑着问",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "秋水兄弟，你们是怎样和‘权力帮’结下的梁子，且说来听听。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_da",
      "speaker_name": "唐大",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "以‘权力帮’的惯例，向来是鸡犬不留的，而且行动极其迅速。秋水兄弟回得剑庐，只怕他们也跟上来了。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼闷声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哼，不死算他大命。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "speaker_name": "康出渔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "萧大侠，此时此地，责怪已无用，反正己与‘权力帮’对上了，我们先商议一下对策。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我放信鸽，再命人紧急通知桂林孟师弟。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "speaker_name": "康出渔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我可以去请几个朋友，辛虎丘最肯助人。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_da",
      "speaker_name": "唐大突然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别忘记辛虎丘的知交是孔扬秦。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_da",
      "speaker_name": "唐大突然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "九天十地，十九人魔中有一位‘三绝剑魔’，如果我没有弄错，便是这孔扬秦！我这是听唐朋说的。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_da",
      "speaker_name": "唐大",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唐刚还在襄阳，不然真可以请他来；唐方行踪不定过几天可能会路过锦江。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "speaker_name": "康出渔忽然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只怕日未落尽，鸟已死荆",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "speaker_name": "康出渔忽然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "鸟声是突然静止的。",
      "tone": null,
      "chapter": 4
    }
